    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. The exterior shows significant signs of age, including heavy rust along the rocker panels and a few noticeable dents on the rear bumper. Mechanically, the engine requires immediate attention as it struggles to idle and there is a known leak in the transmission fluid line. The interior has seen better days, with several tears in the upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is being sold strictly as-is, and towing is recommended.",
